node_7.description: This is Isabella Rodriguez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, open Hobbs Cafe at 8:00 am, work at the counter until 4:00 pm, gather party material for Valentine's Day party at 4:30 pm, switch on the furnace and TV at 5:00 pm, invite customers to join the party at 5:30 pm, continue working at the counter until 8:00 pm, close the cafe at 8:00 pm.
